            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>drained tortelloni </strong>and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>(save the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>into the sauce<strong> </strong>and give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is nicely coated – this is your <strong>sausage meatball & tomato sauce with tomato & mozzarella tortelloni</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
